OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru has pushed for fairer
OL,7,Ffunding for Wales from a Westminster
OL,8,Fgovernment and Welsh independence as
OL,9,Fthey released their manifesto
OL,11,F"For Fairness, For Ambition, For
OL,12,FWales" reads the cover of Plaid
OL,13,FCymru's green manifesto booklet.
OL,15,FInside is a pledge to demand "fair
OL,16,Ffunding" for Wales from Westminster.
