OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FIts leader, Rhun ap Iorwerth, says 14
OL,7,Fyears of Tory cuts and "weak
OL,8,Fopposition" from Labour means only
OL,9,FPlaid Cymru offers a "real
OL,10,Falternative" in Wales.
OL,12,FITV News Wales Reporter Rhys Williams
OL,13,Fexplains what Plaid Cymru is proposing
OL,14,Fto offer voters after launching its
OL,15,FGeneral Election manifesto
OL,17,FThe manifesto contains six headline
OL,18,Fpledges:
