OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,F1. Secure the #4bn owed to Wales from
OL,7,FHS2 to invest in improving public
OL,8,Ftransport infrastructure and reverse
OL,9,Flocal bus cuts.
OL,11,F2. Demand a fair funding system for
OL,12,FWales, "based around our needs, giving
OL,13,Fus the public services we deserve."
OL,15,F3. Recruit 500 GPs into Wales through
OL,16,F"fair funding from Westminster."
OL,18,F4. A new cancer strategy to ensure
OL,19,Fcancers are caught and treated
OL,20,Fearlier, and ending Wales' postcode
OL,21,Flottery for treatment.
