OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,F5. Increasing child benefit by #20 per
OL,7,Fweek to lift 60,000 Welsh children out
OL,8,Fof poverty.
OL,10,F6. Devolving the Crown Estate and use
OL,11,Fthe proceeds (and windfall taxes) to
OL,12,Fcreate green jobs.
OL,14,FThis is clearly a primarily economic
OL,15,Fpitch to Welsh voters from Plaid
OL,16,FCymru. Many of the promises are based
OL,17,Fon the scrapping of the Barnett
OL,18,FFormula - the system by which money is
OL,19,Fallocated to governments in Cardiff,
OL,20,FEdinburgh and Belfast.
