OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FMr ap Iorwerth told journalists his
OL,7,Fparty is the only one advocating for
OL,8,Fthe abolition of the formula in favour
OL,9,Fof a "needs-based model."
OL,11,FOn a similar theme, Plaid Cymru is
OL,12,Fpledging to secure the #4bn it says is
OL,13,Fowed to Wales from the building of HS2.
OL,15,FThis is because the UK government
OL,16,Fclassified the London to Birmingham
OL,17,Fline as an "England and Wales"
OL,18,Fproject, rather than an "England only"
OL,19,Fproject.
