OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FWere Wales to be treated in line with
OL,7,Fboth Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fthrough the Barnett Formula on HS2
OL,9,Ffunding, Wales would receive #3.9bn in
OL,10,Fconsequential cash.
OL,12,FThis is a call also made by both the
OL,13,FWelsh Conservatives and Welsh Labour,
OL,14,Fbut the UK Government has rejected the
OL,15,Fdemand.
OL,17,FBoth Labour leader Sir Keir Starmer
OL,18,Fand Shadow Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,19,Fhave refused to commit to releasing
OL,20,Fthe cash to Cardiff.
