OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FThe party promises to prepare a Green
OL,7,FPaper on the path to independence, but
OL,8,Fit takes 42 pages of the manifesto
OL,9,Fbefore the subject is mentioned in any
OL,10,Fdetail.
OL,12,FThat decision perhaps comes as no
OL,13,Fsurprise when a recent poll showed
OL,14,Findependence was only the 15th most
OL,15,Fimportant subject mentioned by Welsh
OL,16,Fvoters.
