OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FOther highlights from Plaid's
OL,7,Fmanifesto include a pledge to re-
OL,8,Fintroduce a cap on bankers' bonuses
OL,9,Fand to equalise capital gains tax with
OL,10,Fincome tax. The party is also
OL,11,Fpromising to support the introduction
OL,12,Fof a "wealth tax".
OL,14,FPlaid is promising a "Welsh Green New
OL,15,FDeal" creating "rewarding, meaningful
OL,16,Fand fair work" in the emerging green
OL,17,Fand net-zero sector.
