OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FIn this chapter, the manifesto calls
OL,7,Fon the UK Government to "nationalise
OL,8,Fthe Port Talbot steelworks" (the UK's
OL,9,Fsingle biggest carbon polluter), and
OL,10,Ffailing that, the Welsh Government
OL,11,Fshould explore a compulsory purchase
OL,12,Fof the plant while future options for
OL,13,Fmaking steel production greener are
OL,14,Fdeveloped.
