OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FOne of Plaid's headline promises is to
OL,7,Ftake full control over the Crown
OL,8,FEstate in Wales. The estate has
OL,9,Falready been devolved to Scotland, and
OL,10,FPlaid say the proceeds of energy
OL,11,Fprojects, including offshore wind
OL,12,Ffarms, should flow to the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment, rather than to Westminster.
OL,15,FPlaid Cymru tend to find general
OL,16,Felections difficult. History shows
OL,17,Fmany of the voters who lend them their
OL,18,Fvotes in Senedd Elections defect to
OL,19,FLabour or the Conservatives in UK-wide
OL,20,Fpolls.
