OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FThis means that the party has failed
OL,7,Fto make inroads beyond its traditional
OL,8,Fheartlands in the west of the country
OL,9,Fin general elections.
OL,11,FThis time around, merely maintaining
OL,12,Fthe four seats Plaid currently hold in
OL,13,FWestminster will be challenging
OL,14,Fbecause constituency boundaries have
OL,15,Fbeen changed in Wales, and the party
OL,16,Fare arguably the biggest losers.
